{
  "texts": [
    "In future research, optimization could be continued through several approaches.",
    "First, it will be necessary to further refine the foundational large models, particularly by upgrading them to multimodal models.",
    "This is crucial, as many patients with clinical brain injury may not be able to complete typing or speaking tasks.",
    "Utilizing various input modes (such as voice and images) can help to broaden accessibility.",
    "Second, further studies should explore whether agents based on medical guidelines exhibit common patterns in other conditions, such as rare diseases or critical illnesses."
  ]
}